---
// Componente de Iniciativas
---

<section id="iniciativas" class="section iniciativas-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <h2>Nuestras Iniciativas</h2>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="iniciativas-grid">
      <div class="iniciativa-card">
        <div class="iniciativa-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Divulgación en redes</h3>
        <p>Contenido educativo y de interés en varias plataformas. Videos cortos, memes, infografías, ensayos...</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="iniciativa-card">
        <div class="iniciativa-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"></path>
            <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"></line>
            <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Conversatorios</h3>
        <p>Un espacio de diálogo e intercambio de conocimientos donde expertos y público dialogan sobre temas relevantes.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="iniciativa-card">
        <div class="iniciativa-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path>
            <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Talleres</h3>
        <p>Un espacio práctico de aprendizaje donde experimentarás con ciencia y tecnología mediante actividades guiadas por expertos.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .iniciativas-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    padding: var(--spacing-xxl) 0;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }
  
  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  
  .section-divider {
    height: 4px;
    width: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-secondary), var(--color-accent));
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-sm);
  }
  
  .iniciativas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
  }
  
  .iniciativa-card {
    background-color: var(--color-card-bg);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .iniciativa-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  
  .iniciativa-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background-color: var(--color-secondary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-md);
  }
  
  .iniciativa-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .iniciativa-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .iniciativas-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>